_sText:
cs_night_borough is a port of the cs_night_borough from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

Funny billboard, building, and bus stop ads are scattered throughout the map. 

Some are brands that I modified and parodied (Grey Van shades, Lesswiser beer, Redbook footwear,...) 

while others are my original idea/work that I designed and created from scratch 

(Crook law firm, LOL insurance, Family jewels,...). 

Many others will be discovered while roaming the streets.
